                     <interp inst="t18460511-1194-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 70lbs. weight of flock, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and 1 bag, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18460511-name-1100" type="victimName">
